ask the user quote which number's table do you want and save to num.
ask the user quote how many times and save to limit.

let xsign be the word x.
let eqsign be the word =.

let counter be the number 1.
keep doing the following while counter is at most limit.
    let result be num times counter.
    say num and xsign and counter and eqsign and result.
    increase counter by 1.
end keep.